{
  "text": "The following result is proved in [16, §3] (for the n ij ), but we include a proof for the convenience of the reader. We also note that a connection between frieze patterns and cluster algebras was first explicitly given in [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "16223802"
